<HL>
   Recycling Waste Is Gaining Popularity
   Among Americans, Group's Poll Shows
   ----
   By Bill Paul
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B3B
</SO>
